    "A www.ijacsa.thesai.org score of 1 indicates total agreement between reference and candidate text.3) BERTScore: BERTScore is an automatic evaluation metric in text generation tasks that evaluates the similarity of each candidate sentence token to each reference sentence token by means of contextual embeddings [23].",
